Package model.arena.entities

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Entities
    This interface describes any entities that are in the @Arena.
    EntitiesVisitor
    This is the core of the Visitor Pattern that recognize the entity that call the method visit and then communicate with the @Arena.
    Hero
    This interface added only one method because the hero implements both interfaces and this is only for him.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bullet
    This son of the Entity define a bullet that cannot shoot and have to hurt at the contact damage.
    Entities.Builder
    This tool allow you to create an entity like a "stream" and do the right control in order to instance the right entity that you want and call the right constructor of the implementation of Entities.
    EntitiesImpl
    This is the primitive implementation of the Entities interface because is the most generic entity.
    EntitiesVisitorImpl
    This instance call the @Arena with the right method @add.
    HeroImpl
    This is the instance of the hero and has a particular features that the others haven't.
    Point
    This class is used to localize the entities in the Arena.
    Position
    This class decorated the @Point, the @Directions and the @Dimension.
